gossip.h3_f:
advertisement = {pubkey, endpoint, advertised_at}
sig = Ed25519-Sign(pubkey_priv, CBOR(advertisement))
gossip payload: [..., {ad, sig}, ...]

receiver: verify sig against ad.pubkey → store iff ok
additional: PoW of 2^18 leading zeros on {pubkey, endpoint}

stealth.h2_f:
ClientHello bytes = chrome_120_template with {
  random = our random,
  server_name = our hostname (or ECH-wrapped),
  session_id = our session id,
}
JA4 = t13d_xxxx_xxxx_xxxx   (matches current Chrome stable)

stealth.h4_f:
DoH:   POST https://cloudflare-dns.com/dns-query   {name: x.vortexx.sol}
ECH:   ClientHello.extensions += encrypted_sni(public_key_from_HTTPS_record)
