x25519.h1_f:
private key: a ∈ [0, 2²⁵⁵)   (32 bytes little-endian, clamped)
public key:  A = a · G            (32-byte compressed point)
shared:      s = a · B = b · A    (32 bytes, → HKDF input)
performance: ~100 µs per DH on an iPhone 11
